ttp://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was the first time Britain had a men's football team competing at the Olympics since 1960 and, interestingly, there has not been once since in 2016, 2020 or 2024.\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 552, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 409, \"end\": 416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999125045086473, \"rank\": 8.738573313630182e-05, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was a Team GB women's football team at Tokyo 2020 - who suffered defeat to Australia in the quarter-finals - but there will not be one at Paris 2024 this year.\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 566, \"end\": 573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_Olympic_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9686045099944406, \"rank\": 0.03202906554581259, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_Olympic_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_Olympic_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 599, \"end\": 604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999932652829, \"rank\": 6.734698169461801e-08, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 635, \"end\": 644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.7587259301086346, \"rank\": 0.3179418145648843, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 698, \"end\": 708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.961709878584135e-24, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read on to find out why there is no British teams competing in the Olympic football competitions in both the men's and women's events\\u2026  There is no Team GB team in the Olympic men's football competition at the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 757, \"end\": 764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999772547829868, \"rank\": 2.2729758692797415e-05, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Metro's Head of Sport James Goldman delivers punchy analysis, transfer talk and his take on the week's biggest stories direct to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 1096, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 967, \"end\": 980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Goldman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"James Goldman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q28389\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Goldman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Goldman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign up here, it's an open goal.\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1130, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Football has been contested at every Summer Olympics since 1900, bar the 1932 Games.\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1216, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic football falls under the jurisdiction of the International Olympic Committee (IOC) rather than FIFA, which governs both the World Cup and Euros.\", \"from\