 \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1521, \"end\": 1529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999668343668, \"rank\": 2.3739918734248806e-08, \"text\": \"Scotland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1534, \"end\": 1550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999985675458, \"rank\": 1.4324991539850413e-09, \"text\": \"Northern Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the issue is that the IOC, unlike FIFA, classifies Britain as one entity - which saw Scotland, Wales and Northern Ireland walk away in 1960 - amid fears their participation at the Olympics could threaten their status in FIFA-run competitions.\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1799, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1579, \"end\": 1582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.636533963605049e-22, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1591, \"end\": 1595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"score\": 0.8440190206211581, \"rank\": 0.1846178612388291, \"text\": \"FIFA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\"}, 