pedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is also no Team GB team in the Olympic women's football competition at the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2204, \"end\": 2211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_Olympic_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9686045099944406, \"rank\": 0.03202906554581259, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_Olympic_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_Olympic_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike the men's team, Scottish players featured in the most recent squad, including Caroline Weir and Kim Little for the 2020 Games in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2424, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2305, \"end\": 2313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_in_Scotland\", \"score\": 0.9857525904964859, \"rank\": 0.013745902384077874, \"text\": \"Scottish\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_in_Scotland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_in_Scotland\"}, {\"begin\": 2367, \"end\": 2380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Weir\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caroline Weir\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Weir\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Weir\"}, {\"begin\": 2385, \"end\": 2395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Little\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kim Little\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Little\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Little\"}, {\"begin\": 2418, \"end\": 2423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999326